{"word":"ἐκπυνθάνομαι","slug":"ἐκπυνθάνομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐκπυνθάνομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-πεύσομαι</el>) (aor2 <el>ἐξεπῠθόμην</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>: <i>to search out, make enquiry</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to enquire about, hear of, learn</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>; <el>ἐκπ. τινος</el> <i>to make inquiry of</i> him, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}